                  <h3>How soon can a technician come to fix my refrigerator?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>We understand the importance of a working refrigerator. You can schedule a same-day appointment, or choose a time that fits your needs best.</p>
