              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>What is the diagnostic cost for refrigerator repair?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Our diagnostic fee is $89, covering a comprehensive assessment to identify the problem accurately.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>Do you use original parts for refrigerator repairs?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Yes, we use only high-quality, original parts from trusted suppliers, backed by warranties starting at 3 months. Our commitment to quality parts ensures reliable, lasting repairs.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>How much will it cost to repair my refrigerator?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>While we provide transparent pricing, we can only give an accurate quote after a full diagnostic. Refrigerators often require detailed inspection to determine the underlying issues. Once diagnosed, we’ll provide an exact quote covering parts and labor.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>How long will it take to repair my refrigerator?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Most common refrigerator issues can be resolved on the same day, as our technicians carry essential parts with them. For any specialized parts required, delivery is typically within 2-3 days, so we can complete the repair promptly.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>Is the service fee waived if I approve the repair?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Yes, if you approve the repair, we waive the service fee to keep your overall repair costs down.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>Do you provide a warranty on labor for refrigerator repairs?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Absolutely. We offer a standard 3-month warranty on labor, and for more extensive repairs such as compressor or condenser work, we provide a 1-year warranty.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>Are your technicians certified to handle refrigerants?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Yes, all our technicians hold universal EPA-608 certification and have hands-on experience handling refrigerants like R134, R600, and others commonly used in refrigerators.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>If my refrigerator is working fine, do I still need maintenance?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Yes, regular maintenance is crucial for preventing unexpected breakdowns. Even a thin dust layer on condenser coils can cause your refrigerator to work harder, increasing wear on the compressor and shortening its lifespan. Routine maintenance keeps your unit efficient and helps prevent costly repairs.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>My refrigerator is quite old. Should I still consider repairs?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>If the fridge’s exterior and interior components are in good shape, repairs are often more economical than replacement. Our technicians can assess its overall condition and provide guidance on the best option for you.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>I don’t know my refrigerator’s brand or model. Can you still help?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Absolutely! Our technicians are experienced with all major brands and models. Even without the brand or model sticker, we can identify your unit through inspection.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>Another company diagnosed the problem but didn’t repair it. Can you help?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>We prefer to conduct our own diagnostic to ensure accuracy. If the previous diagnosis was unclear, our technician will provide a thorough assessment and repair plan so you’re fully informed before proceeding.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>What does the final repair price include?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>We offer full transparency on repair costs. The final price includes labor and any necessary parts, with a clear explanation provided by our technician before any work begins.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
                <div class="fa">
                  <h3>My location isn’t listed on your website. Can you still help?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="fa_plus">︾</div>
                <div class="fa_minus">︽</div>
              </div>
              <div class="questions">
                <p>Please give us a call! We serve a wide area and will do our best to connect you with the closest available technician.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="FAQ">
